      "role": "user",
      "content": "i feel like i’m just stuck in this same shitty pattern over and over again. every time i think i’ve finally turned things around, i just end up right back at zero. lost the job, lost the girl, lost everything. it’s like i’m just looping through the same failures and there’s no way out. i’m just so tired of trying.",
