    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that’s the thing, it’s not just a bad phase. it’s a pattern. it’s like i’m hardwired this way. no matter what \"small shift\" i make, the gravity of my own life just pulls me back down to the same spot. i've tried the shifts, i've tried the help. it doesn't matter. the loop only ends one way.",
