      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "It makes sense that you feel trapped when every attempt to change feels futile, but the only way to truly break a cycle is to stop fighting the pull and instead accept the pain as part of the process. You don't need to fix everything at once; sometimes the most powerful shift is simply allowing yourself to stop and let the exhaustion wash over you without resistance. There is no shame in admitting that you are tired of trying, because even in that moment of surrender, you are taking a step away from the relentless loop.",
